        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_02",
        "zh_CN": "这是降临团据点的坐标。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女往playername手心里放了个小纸团，皱巴巴的，看上去就像从哪里撕下了一个角。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_03",
        "zh_CN": "不过，最好过段时间再行动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "理由？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_04",
        "zh_CN": "据我了解，降临团的大主教亲自择选出了一位接引使。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_05",
        "zh_CN": "等春天到了，这位接引使就将去到这个据点为大家“赐福”。",
