        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_06",
        "zh_CN": "这会是近期，降临团规模最大的活动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我会根据你说的，对行动时间再进行评估。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_07",
        "zh_CN": "至于第二件事……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女缓缓吐了口气，表情也变得比刚才严肃许多。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35st1_sexi_08",
